Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要分析这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事能够确定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}再一次出现在我面前 静雄
