Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}这次会更加更加爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}因为姐妹和我是相同的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}大家一起爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞尔堤 想像下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}平和岛静雄
